@startuml
[*] --> Login
Login --> DisplayMainArea : after user signs in
DisplayMainArea --> ShowMarketConditions : user selects market conditions
ShowMarketConditions --> ShowMarketReport : customer selects market report
DisplayMainArea --> RequirePhotoForPestControl : users choose pest control help
RequirePhotoForPestControl --> ShowPestControlTechniques : customer selects pest control techniques
DisplayMainArea --> ProvideSoilSuggestions : receiving soil information from user
ProvideSoilSuggestions --> OfferWeatherInsights : provided location
OfferWeatherInsights --> DisplayLabourAvailability : receiving a location from user
DisplayMainArea --> ContinueUsingService : viewing any of these results
ContinueUsingService --> EndSession : user logs out
@enduml
